Use Emotion for stylizing components through a CSS class.

- https://emotion.sh/docs/introduction

Basic components

- [x] HGroup
- [x] VGroup
- [x] Label
- [x] Button
- [x] Icon button
  - [x] Arrow button
- [x] Container
- [x] ContextMenu
- [x] Select
- [x] TextInput
- [ ] CheckBox
  - [ ] RTL
- [ ] LoadingBar (consists of horizontally moving dots)
- [ ] FormItem
  - A horizontal group generally containing of a label and a form control.
  - [ ] RTL
- [ ] Tile container
  - [ ] Live tiles
  - [ ] Bottom bar (triggered on right click or long touch pressure)

